    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014it's been well-loved and looked after, so you're getting a great car that's ready for many more adventures! Everything runs smoothly and it still looks fantastic out on the road. It's the perfect fit if you're looking for something reliable and comfy that\u2019s ready to go today. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM valvetrain. Mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain is complemented by a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal torque vectoring. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. The chassis maintains communicative feedback with refreshed bushings and dampers. A true driver\u2019s machine, mechanically robust and tuned for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Well-maintained engine and clean interior. Minor cosmetic wear. Runs reliably. Clean title in hand.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking reliability and style without the new-car premium. It has been treated with care, evidenced by a spotless interior and a service history that is current and documented. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts crisply, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. While there are some minor, expected signs of use\u2014such as light swirl marks in the clear coat and small chips on the hood from normal road travel\u2014the overall aesthetic remains sharp and professional. The cabin is free of odors or stains, and every feature, from the heated seats to the premium audio system, works exactly as intended. Recently fitted with new tires and fresh fluids, this car is fully prepared for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical reliability and sophisticated engineering. This selection has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for performance and safety. Boasting a well-preserved interior and a consistent service history, this motorcar offers an exceptional balance of luxury and long-term value. We invite discerning buyers to experience the superior road manners and enduring quality of this distinguished professional offering.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly loved? This beauty is in great shape and ready to hit the road with its next owner! It\u2019s super clean, runs like a dream, and has plenty of life left in it. It's been well-cared for and is perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six power plant and a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The mechanical heart of this vehicle remains potent, with the individual throttle bodies providing instantaneous response and the Vanos variable valve timing system operating within factory parameters. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including the reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points and a comprehensive cooling system refresh. The chassis retains its signature balance thanks to a functional M-variable differential lock and well-damped MacPherson/multi-link suspension. A mechanically sound, driver-focused example with a detailed service log.",
      "price": 34500.0,
